Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.10,0:00:23.47,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}无止境的旅途中  止步不前之时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.47,0:00:29.74,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}我们深深地叹气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.80,0:00:37.43,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}再次放开了紧握的手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.90,0:00:44.86,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}但是现在已经没有什么可怕的了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.44,0:00:52.79,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}连接心灵之间那坚固的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.79,0:00:58.25,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}决不会被斩断
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.30,0:01:07.98,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}继续寻求 终于找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.98,0:01:13.77,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}在这个地方画上句号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.92,0:01:23.06,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}悲伤与愤怒 化为力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.06,0:01:28.02,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}命运就在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:00.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.30,0:22:19.27,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}本是没有交点的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.27,0:22:20.05,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}今天也
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.05,0:22:24.91,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}企图夺走我们的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.54,0:22:30.49,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}即使获得了想要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.49,0:22:31.49,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为什么却
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.49,0:22:36.47,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}无法坦率地会心一笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.12,0:22:42.17,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}流出的眼泪    不代表弱小或后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.85,0:22:46.99,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}只是孕育痛苦的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.65,0:22:52.03,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不论什么样的瞬间与命运
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.03,0:23:00.78,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}终于明白了唯一可以确定的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.78,0:23:03.33,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}极限也好  困难也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.33,0:23:07.32,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都不愿意放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.32,0:23:12.21,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就这样决不放手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.21,0:23:20.04,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}紧握你的右手传来的温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.04,0:23:23.71,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,750)\blur2}就在这里


Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.39,0:01:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是这个表现 小梅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:01:54.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这的确是表示金子的意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.43,0:01:56.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.54,0:02:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在调查是不是有隐藏的暗号
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.14,0:02:02.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗号？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.44,0:02:07.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼金术为了不让一般人轻松解读
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.51,0:02:11.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会用比喻或者寓意来隐藏内容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.66,0:02:15.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这本研究书一眼看去没有这个特征
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.62,0:02:20.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就着眼于金子和长生不老之类出现较多的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.10,0:02:23.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,改变一下调查方法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.37,0:02:25.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后知道什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.73,0:02:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.64,0:02:31.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.55,0:02:32.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.16,0:02:32.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:33.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.18,0:02:35.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果意识无法恢复的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.30,0:02:37.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不知道怎么办了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.27,0:02:40.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 让你担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:44.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 为什么我被分解了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:48.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.12,0:02:50.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使想要扛着你移动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.93,0:02:52.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.12,0:02:54.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以分解了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.50,0:02:56.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.96,0:02:59.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给大家添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.62,0:03:01.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前也有过类似的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.98,0:03:04.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 来这里之前也有过一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.53,0:03:11.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在分解的状态下 你也不太方便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.82,0:03:14.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先帮你复原吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.45,0:03:16.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.53,0:03:18.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我拿一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.23,0:03:21.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:25.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.46,0:03:27.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是右手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢 不能拼错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.30,0:03:35.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分解…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.55,0:03:37.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,组合…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:50.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 小梅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.20,0:03:53.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你干了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.61,0:03:55.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.14,0:04:01.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,改变组合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.15,0:04:04.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把金什么的长生不老什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.31,0:04:08.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同样的地方重叠起来会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.93,0:04:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“金的人”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.78,0:04:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个单词你那边也有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.21,0:04:22.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“不死”和这边重复
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“完全的人”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:26.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 有了有了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.51,0:04:29.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那页给我 马可
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.75,0:04:31.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个和这里连上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:32.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有“黄金之人”吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.97,0:04:34.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:40.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是最后一张了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.95,0:04:48.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.07,0:04:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.57,0:05:03.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国土炼成阵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.05,0:05:07.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今知道这个有什么用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.89,0:05:12.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道这本研究书完全没用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.84,0:05:14.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.37,0:05:14.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.19,0:05:17.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这个国家会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:19.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.19,0:05:22.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把扭转这个危机状况的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.60,0:05:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寄托在别人的研究上的我太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.78,0:05:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长 想告诉我的就是这件事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:37.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是兄长的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.16,0:05:40.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是应该看到了更远的前方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.13,0:05:43.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.65,0:05:47.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使分解也无法注意到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:49.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.58,0:05:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使还隐藏着什么也不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.10,0:05:55.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.81,0:06:06.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你小子 在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.72,0:06:08.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这该死的天气不好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.88,0:06:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使没那么冷 我也是怕冷的类型
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:12.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁管你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.49,0:06:16.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道哪边是正面哪边是反面了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 都被翻过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.29,0:06:23.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.58,0:06:26.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扭转危机状况
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.60,0:06:28.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把刚才的图…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.87,0:06:31.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正反翻转
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.00,0:06:41.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.96,0:06:43.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说中了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.93,0:06:48.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是融合了炼丹术才能发动的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.96,0:06:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新的亚美斯多利斯国土炼成阵

Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.37,0:07:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎没有人通过的痕迹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.74,0:07:13.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走错路了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.49,0:07:15.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.77,0:07:52.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.77,0:07:57.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了搬出斯洛乌斯挖掘通道后留下的碎石
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.69,0:07:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而使用了这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.21,0:08:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是红莲之炼金术师吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.23,0:08:08.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:10.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是普莱德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.86,0:08:13.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找我有什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.61,0:08:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯卡这事怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.12,0:08:18.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在正在追踪中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.33,0:08:20.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先放一边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.82,0:08:24.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先在布里克斯刻下血之纹章
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.18,0:08:26.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恕我直言
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.79,0:08:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布里克斯兵的团结犹如磐石 所以非常强大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.41,0:08:33.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没法简单地办到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:36.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就利用那份强大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.88,0:08:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯洛乌斯在挖掘的通道马上就要完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:48.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.76,0:08:51.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让我来刻下血之纹章吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:54.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在布里克斯要塞里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.00,0:09:09.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等候多时了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.00,0:09:11.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么变化吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:13.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有什么特别的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.66,0:09:17.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说金普利下落不明 真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.07,0:09:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.68,0:09:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了让矿道塌方的爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,0:09:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金普利及其数名部下下落不明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:29.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仔细搜索了 结果没发现任何人的尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.94,0:09:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他数名是指布里克斯兵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.83,0:09:39.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是指金普利的部下两人和…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.41,0:09:43.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.57,0:09:51.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 钢之大将吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.18,0:09:53.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望他没事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.94,0:09:57.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西边怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.21,0:09:59.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还能怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.70,0:10:02.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和班戴鲁顿国境战非常残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.44,0:10:06.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那战斗方法简直是故意在产生战死者一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.08,0:10:10.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.55,0:10:12.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,军队为了制作炼成阵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.28,0:10:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带头挑起流血事件
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.53,0:10:18.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,南边的菲利曹长有联络吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.29,0:10:21.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前 有过一次电话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.89,0:10:26.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在佛特赛特南部和阿耶鲁戈军激烈交火
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.17,0:10:45.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑 汤玛斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.82,0:10:47.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别停下 托马…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.46,0:10:56.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.58,0:10:57.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要活下来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.18,0:11:00.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对要活下来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.14,0:11:06.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.30,0:11:08.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们原马斯坦古组
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.11,0:11:10.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使没有这战争 也是被憎恨的物件
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和大佐联系过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.39,0:11:17.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 通过阿姆斯壮家的信使
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.23,0:11:18.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,断断续续地…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.21,0:11:21.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.55,0:11:24.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北方也很严重吧 注意点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.64,0:11:27.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是很严重吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.36,0:11:31.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想把这个国家变成地狱的家伙的手下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.21,0:11:34.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺利进行着他们的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.27,0:11:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我们却完全无法出手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:52.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.96,0:11:59.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以不用再挖了吧？普莱德
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.56,0:12:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.69,0:12:09.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一天就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.33,0:12:22.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 当心点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.11,0:12:28.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.82,0:12:31.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.47,0:12:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来排队
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.29,0:12:37.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗赛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.22,0:12:40.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我下次想吃肉馅派呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.16,0:12:43.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有材料的话就做哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.55,0:12:44.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我期待着哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.53,0:12:49.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我虽然没干活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.42,0:12:53.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是这两个孩子也好 能不能分点吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.89,0:12:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.74,0:12:56.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老婆婆也不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.33,0:13:02.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来很好吃的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.30,0:13:04.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小罗塞 给我盛一大碗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.77,0:13:06.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.40,0:13:08.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家平等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.31,0:13:10.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.55,0:13:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.86,0:13:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能…能不能也给我一点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.32,0:13:23.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.48,0:13:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.11,0:13:29.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你从哪来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.66,0:13:32.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没法说是从哪里 我到处乱走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.19,0:13:37.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到这里来干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.70,0:13:38.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.15,0:13:40.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里发生过的暴动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.86,0:13:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那个原因这里变成了一座废墟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:50.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明有这么好吃的食物？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:56.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能这么说我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.50,0:14:01.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也只能做这么多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.58,0:14:03.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.17,0:14:07.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,热烘烘的午饭和小姐的笑脸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.46,0:14:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为了大家的动力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.66,0:14:15.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.62,0:14:19.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受了你们照顾还想拜托事有点过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.68,0:14:21.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 我正在寻找教会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.58,0:14:23.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教会？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.92,0:14:24.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:28.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为暴动原因的雷托教本部
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:39.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如你所见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.79,0:14:41.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今 即使下去也什么都没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.66,0:14:44.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有通往地下的通道吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.37,0:14:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 确实有 不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.26,0:14:54.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.64,0:14:56.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毒水
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.37,0:14:59.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知什么时候变成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.96,0:15:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来普通的人类无法前进呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.14,0:15:10.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.65,0:15:11.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.52,0:15:12.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进去的话会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.11,0:15:22.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇蹟之术…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.85,0:15:28.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 是炼金术吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:31.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到里面去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.69,0:15:32.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们能等我一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.60,0:15:53.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.67,0:15:55.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.08,0:15:58.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做了个夸张的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.54,0:16:05.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一上来就中了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.79,0:16:26.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,障碍不了它吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.49,0:16:27.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.08,0:16:31.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试试关住它看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.68,0:16:46.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这真让人头痛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.33,0:16:51.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.17,0:17:05.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.18,0:17:06.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不攻过来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.45,0:17:10.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.18,0:17:12.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是冯·霍恩海姆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.59,0:17:17.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你的容器到这里为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.18,0:17:22.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离开这里就会死吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.84,0:17:27.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超越一定的界线就会死吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:30.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就和那时的烧瓶小人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.62,0:17:37.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你只能在这个通道和中央都市的中心部活动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.56,0:17:39.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.89,0:17:43.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说中了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.65,0:17:46.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.30,0:17:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说点什么如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.98,0:17:50.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个家里蹲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.70,0:17:55.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在生气？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.91,0:17:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愤怒什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:17:59.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不存于我的体内
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.57,0:18:03.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只是愤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.00,0:18:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把不需要的感情留在父亲大人那里了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.75,0:18:09.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字是普莱德
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.90,0:18:12.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普莱德
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.86,0:18:15.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 是“傲慢”吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.30,0:18:20.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人有七宗罪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.73,0:18:22.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,色欲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.78,0:18:24.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贪婪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.71,0:18:26.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怠惰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:28.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暴食
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.35,0:18:30.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嫉妒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.38,0:18:32.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.86,0:18:36.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后是…傲慢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.24,0:18:40.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他最早分离的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.23,0:18:43.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普莱德呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.39,0:18:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且以烧瓶中的姿态分离
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.53,0:18:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个样子才是傲慢并且自尊心强的那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.72,0:18:57.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你父亲的本质吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.56,0:19:01.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到父亲大人这里来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.16,0:19:04.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别着急
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.16,0:19:06.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使你不叫我 我也会去的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.20,0:19:09.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去告诉那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:12.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奴隶23号不久就会去找他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.37,0:19:19.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在中央都市摆着架子等着我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.62,0:19:24.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我等着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:28.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冯·霍恩海姆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.49,0:19:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.19,0:19:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面有什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.78,0:19:50.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 一般人还是别接近比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.69,0:19:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.02,0:19:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去告诉大家千万不要进去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:02.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您去里面干了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.04,0:20:08.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去宣战了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.08,0:20:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交换了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.22,0:20:15.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.03,0:20:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在暴风雪中真是很累
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.72,0:20:22.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去喝杯难喝的咖啡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.82,0:20:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.11,0:20:32.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.19,0:20:35.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…那是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:38.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是德拉古马
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.93,0:20:44.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北方的德拉古马发出开战宣言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.41,0:20:46.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全员进入战斗准备
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.41,0:20:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重复
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.45,0:20:50.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北方的德拉古马发出开战宣言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.11,0:20:52.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全员战斗准备
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.11,0:21:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布里克斯的北壁 不在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.69,0:21:11.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是求之不得的好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.16,0:21:14.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 金普利先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.16,0:21:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加上我有很多部下在要塞里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.76,0:21:22.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗开始的话就能在内部接应
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.46,0:21:25.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让要塞陷入混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.97,0:21:32.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我德拉古马长年无法越过的布里克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.94,0:21:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就让我攻占下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.69,0:21:38.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 宣战了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.76,0:21:42.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放个盛大的烟花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.30,0:21:43.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全炮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.45,0:21:45.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备发射
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.38,0:21:56.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.36,0:23:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.74,0:23:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字是赞帕诺
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.77,0:23:36.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是金普利的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.57,0:23:40.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马可医生潜伏在阿斯别克的贫民窟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.80,0:23:44.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你告诉我 赞帕诺
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.84,0:23:46.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保证你的生命安全
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.22,0:23:52.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马可
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.44,0:23:56.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始变得有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.33,0:24:01.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毒辣的灵魂带来惨剧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.77,0:24:05.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决断的矜持在身上刻下伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.04,0:24:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 无法回避
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.29,0:24:09.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了重生
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.49,0:24:14.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.12,0:24:15.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.82,0:24:19.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第43话 蚂蚁的一咬
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.48,0:24:22.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当雪原被染红
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.10,0:24:26.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了守护而流淌的鲜血
